urls.title: Here's what it might be like to travel on a double decker airplane seat
urls.description: Airplane seat designer Alejandro Núñez Vicente reckons his double-decker airplane seat could revolutionize budget air travel. CNN went to the 2022 Aircraft Interiors Expo in Hamburg to try it out.
